libfolia
------------------------------------------
This is a C++ Library, developed by Ko van der Sloot, for working with the
Format for Linguistic Annotation (FoLiA). The software is intended for C++
developers, and provides a high-level API to read, manipulate, and create FoLiA
documents. This software is a necessary dependency for various other tools that
use FoLiA.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.1.5-1
  libfolia-devel-2.4-1bl1
  libfolia14-2.4-1bl1
  libgcc1-9.3.0-2
  libicu67-67.1-1
  libstdc++6-9.3.0-2
  libticcutils8-0.24-1bl1
  libxml2-2.9.9-2
  libxml2-devel-2.9.9-2
  pkg-config-1.6.3-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  autoconf-13-1
  automake-11-1
  binutils-2.34+1git.de9c1b7cfe-1
  cygport-0.34.0-1
  gcc-core-9.3.0-2
  gcc-g++-9.3.0-2
  libtool-2.4.6-7
  make-4.3-1

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/LanguageMachines/libfolia

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/LanguageMachines/libfolia/archive/v2.4.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack libfolia-2.4-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./libfolia-2.4-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/libfolia-2.4-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libfolia-2.4-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libfolia14-2.4-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libfolia-devel-2.4-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(libfolia)
  /usr/bin/foliadiff.sh
  /usr/bin/folialint.exe
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/libfolia.README
  /usr/share/doc/libfolia/AUTHORS
  /usr/share/doc/libfolia/COPYING
  /usr/share/doc/libfolia/NEWS
  /usr/share/doc/libfolia/README
  /usr/share/doc/libfolia/TODO
  /usr/share/doc/libfolia/readme.md
  /usr/share/man/man1/folialint.1.gz

(libfolia14)
  /usr/bin/cygfolia-14.dll

(libfolia-devel)
  /usr/include/libfolia/folia.h
  /usr/include/libfolia/folia_document.h
  /usr/include/libfolia/folia_engine.h
  /usr/include/libfolia/folia_impl.h
  /usr/include/libfolia/folia_properties.h
  /usr/include/libfolia/folia_provenance.h
  /usr/include/libfolia/folia_types.h
  /usr/include/libfolia/folia_utils.h
  /usr/lib/libfolia.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/folia.pc

